{"article_id":"ImFQYe5RMkolu5Oi","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"China ' s president , Xi Jinping , has told Donald Trump in a phone call","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that all sides should avoid rhetoric or action","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that would worsen tensions on the Korean peninsula ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"according to Chinese state media .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Reports quoted Xi as saying :","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"\" At present , the relevant parties must maintain restraint","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and avoid words and deeds","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that would exacerbate the tension on the Korean peninsula . \"","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Trump has pushed China to pressure North Korea to halt a nuclear weapons programme","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"that is nearing the capability","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"of targeting the United States .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"China is the North ' s biggest economic partner and source of aid .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Trump on Friday went further to turn the crisis into a personal battle of wills between him and Kim Jong-un ,","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"warning the North Korean leader","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"he would \" truly regret \" hostile acts against US territory or US allies .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"Donald Trump loyalists","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"eager to back up his rhetoric on North Korea","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"The warning came a few hours after an early morning tweet from the president","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that claimed","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"US military options were \" locked and loaded \" for use","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"if Pyongyang \" acted unwisely \" .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The tweet triggered worldwide alarm and a rebuke from the German chancellor , Angela Merkel ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"who said :","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"\" I consider an escalation of rhetoric the wrong answer . \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"But Trump stood by his words","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"when asked about them at his golf resort in New Jersey .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"\" I hope","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"they are going to fully understand the gravity of what I said ,","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"and what I said is what I mean , \"","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"\" Those words are very , very easy to understand . \"","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Trump then issued an ultimatum to Kim Jong-un himself .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"\" This man will not get away with what he ' s doing , \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"\" If he utters one threat in the form of an overt threat ...","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"or if he does anything in respect to Guam or anyplace else","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"that ' s an American territory or an American ally ,","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"he will truly regret it","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"and he will regret it fast . \"","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Boris Johnson , the UK foreign secretary , said on Twitter","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that Britain was working with the US and other countries in the region","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"to end the diplomatic crisis .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"the international community stood \" shoulder to shoulder","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"in ensuring North Korea stops its aggressive acts \" ,","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"adding :","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Boris Johnson","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"( @ BorisJohnson )","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"The North Korean regime is the cause of this problem","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and they must fix it","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"The North Korean leadership has warned","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"it will launch four missiles at the waters around US Pacific territory of Guam as a warning to the US","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"if it persists with its practice sorties by long-range bombers","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"based on the island .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Despite gung-ho language from the US president ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"there was no change in US deployments in the region or a change in the alert status of US forces .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"And it was reported on Friday","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"that the Trump administration had reopened a channel of communication between US and North Korean diplomats at the UN .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"According to the Associated Press ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"the \" New York channel \" had been broken off by North Korea in protest against sanctions in 2016 ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"but it was revived this year between Joseph Yun , the US envoy for North Korea policy , and Pak Song-il , a senior North Korean diplomat at the country ' s UN mission .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"The US state department said","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"it had no comment on the report .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"It had previously been reported that there had been diplomatic contacts about US detainees in North Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"but the new AP account said","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"the talks addressed wider issues ,","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"although such contacts had so far failed to moderate the exchange of threats between the leaders of the two countries .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Asked about the report on Friday ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"Trump said :","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"\" Well , we don ' t want to talk about progress ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"we don ' t want to talk about back channels . \"","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"We want to talk about a country","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"that has misbehaved for many many years","depth":17},{"id":74,"text":"- decades , actually -","depth":17},{"id":75,"text":"through numerous administrations ,","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"and they didn ' t want to take on the issue","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"and I had no choice","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"but to take it on ,","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"and I ' m taking it on .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"And we ' ll either be very , very successful quickly","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"or we ' re going to be very , very successful in a different way , quickly . \"","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"As for Merkel ' s criticism earlier in the day ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"\" Maybe she ' s speaking for Germany ;","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"let her speak for Germany .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"She ' s a friend of mine ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"she ' s a very good person , a very good woman ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"she ' s a friend of Ivanka .","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"Perhaps she is referring to Germany .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"She ' s certainly not referring to the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that I can tell you . \"","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"In his comments , Trump made it clear","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"that domestic political considerations played a role","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"in shaping his rhetoric .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"\" If somebody else uttered the exact same words","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that I uttered ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"they ' d say :","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"' What a great statement , what a wonderful statement , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"\" But I will tell you ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"we have tens of millions of people in this country","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that are so happy with what I am saying ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"because they say ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"' Finally , we have a president","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that ' s sticking up for our nation and frankly , sticking up for our friends and our allies . ' \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Speaking to reporters in California ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"the US defence secretary , James Mattis , said","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"a conflict on the Korean peninsula would be \" catastrophic \"","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"and stressed","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that US diplomats should take the lead","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"in resolving the crisis .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Mattis pointed to a UN security council vote at the weekend for more sanctions against North Korea as a sign","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"that diplomacy was making progress .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Quick guide","depth":3},{"id":115,"text":"Are US defences strong enough","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"to ward off North Korean missiles ?","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Show Hide","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"What kind of anti-missile defences does the US possess ?","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"The US has various anti-missile options , some","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"designed","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"to take down missiles at short-range","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"and others for medium-to-long-range .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"The US relies heavily on the US Patriot missile and the Terminal High-Altitude Area Defence","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"( THAAD ) .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"The US deployed THAAD to South Korea this year","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"to defend against medium-range missiles .","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"There is a three-phased defence system :","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"ground-based missiles on the Korean peninsula ; US naval ships","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"stationed in the Pacific ;","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and two bases in Alaska and California","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"that can launch an estimated 36 interceptors .","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"Is the US system robust enough","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"to stop a North Korean missile attack ?","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"No air defence system offers anything like a complete guarantee of success .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"The Pentagon offer repeated assurances","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that air defence systems would be more than a match for any North Korean attack .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"when missile defence systems have been put to the test over the last few decades ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"the performance has been far from reassuring .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"The US provided anti-missile defence systems to Israel and Saudi Arabia during the First Gulf War as protection against Iraq 's Scud missiles .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"It was initially claimed that they had shot down 41 of 42 missiles","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"fired by Iraq .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"But eventually it was acknowledged that only a few missiles had been hit .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Recent tests of interceptors have provided little comfort","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"- with success rates of around 50 % on average .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"The Pentagon celebrated in May","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"when it destroyed a mock warhead over the Pacific","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"but overall the performance has been spotty .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"Since the newest intercept system was introduced in 2004","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"only four of nine intercept attempts have been successful .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"Of the five tests since 2010 , only two have been successful .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"However , Friday ' s tweet ,","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"sent out by Trump at about 7.30am from his golf resort in Bedminster , New Jersey ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"put the emphasis back on the use of force :","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"Military solutions are now fully in place ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"locked","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"and loaded ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"should North Korea act unwisely .","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"Hopefully Kim Jong Un will find another path !","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"A White House official later played down the significance of the tweet ,","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"there were continuously updated military contingency plans for any global crisis .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"\" This isn ' t anything new , \"","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"the official said ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"according to CNN .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"The contingency plan for war on the Korean peninsula , Oplan 5027 , envisages a build-up of the US military ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"including half the US navy and more than 1,000 aircraft in the region ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"over 90 days .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"More than 200,000 US civilians would also have to be evacuated .","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"Later on Friday morning , the president retweeted US Pacific command ,","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"which had posted pictures of B-1B Lancer heavy bombers on exercises over the Pacific with the Japanese and South Korean air forces on 7 August ,","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"accompanied by text","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"the planes were ready to fulfil the \" ready to fight tonight \" mission of US forces in South Korea ,","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"\" if called upon to do so \" .","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"Trump ' s messages continued a war of words between the president and North Korea","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that ignited on Tuesday","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"when Trump ,","depth":14},{"id":181,"text":"following reports of a breakthrough in Pyongyang ' s weapons programme ,","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"threatened to unleash \" fire and fury","depth":17},{"id":183,"text":"like the world has never seen \"","depth":17},{"id":184,"text":"on North Korea","depth":16},{"id":185,"text":"if the regime continued to threaten the US .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"Kim Jong-un ' s government responded the next day","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"by deriding Trump ' s remarks as a \" lot of nonsense \"","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"and publishing detailed plans","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"to launch missiles","depth":16},{"id":190,"text":"to land in the waters around the US Pacific territory of Guam .","depth":16},{"id":191,"text":"Pyongyang has warned","depth":14},{"id":192,"text":"that continued practice sorties by B-1B bombers over South Korea would trigger the launch of the four Hwasong-12 intermediate-range missiles","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"that would be aimed at the waters around their base on Guam .","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"\" This grave situation requires the KPA","depth":18},{"id":195,"text":"[ Korean People ' s Army ]","depth":18},{"id":196,"text":"to closely watch Guam , the outpost and beachhead for invading the DPRK ,","depth":17},{"id":197,"text":"and necessarily take practical actions of significance","depth":17},{"id":198,"text":"to neutralise it , \"","depth":17},{"id":199,"text":"a KPA spokesman said on the state news service .","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"It added","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"that the missile launch ,","depth":18},{"id":202,"text":"if ordered ,","depth":18},{"id":203,"text":"would aim \" to contain the US major military bases on Guam , including the Andersen air force base ,","depth":18},{"id":204,"text":"in which the US strategic bombers ,","depth":20},{"id":205,"text":"which get on the nerves of the DPRK","depth":21},{"id":206,"text":"and threaten and blackmail it through their frequent visits to the sky above South Korea ,","depth":21},{"id":207,"text":"are stationed ,","depth":19},{"id":208,"text":"and to send a serious warning signal to the US \" .","depth":16},{"id":209,"text":"The B-1 bombers have been modified","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"so as to be non-nuclear capable ,","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"but the North Korean statement identifies them as \" nuclear strategic bombers \" , one of many examples of misperceptions and overheated rhetoric","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"that fog the Korean standoff .","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"\" The United States should think carefully about authorizing further B-1 flights .","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"Leadership may decide to defy the North Korean threat ,","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"but should make that decision consciously","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"and take measures","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"to limit the risk of that action , \"","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"said Adam Mount , an expert on North Korea at the Center for American Progress .","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"The Guam authorities issued new emergency guidelines on Friday","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"that included advice","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"of what to do","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"in the event of a nuclear attack .","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"\" Do not look at the flash or fireball","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"- it can blind you , \"","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"the fact sheet said .","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"\" Take cover behind anything","depth":12},{"id":227,"text":"that might offer protection . \"","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"Asked about the potential for military confrontation ,","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"Mattis told reporters","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"it was his responsibility to prepare \" military options","depth":13},{"id":231,"text":"should they be needed \" .","depth":13},{"id":232,"text":"But he warned :","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"\" The tragedy of war is well enough known ;","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"it doesn ' t need another characterisation , beyond the fact","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"that it would be catastrophic . \"","depth":13},{"id":236,"text":"Alongside its missiles and nuclear warheads , North Korea has thousands of pieces of heavy artillery ,","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"capable of inflicting devastating damage on Seoul .","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"The US has about 35,000 troops","depth":9},{"id":239,"text":"stationed in South Korea","depth":9},{"id":240,"text":"and 40,000 in Japan .","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"They have not been put on a higher alert or redeployed in recent days","depth":9},{"id":242,"text":"despite the heated rhetoric .","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"Malcolm Nance , a former naval intelligence officer , said","depth":10},{"id":244,"text":"that there had been none of the normal indicators of heightened alert at US bases in the region .","depth":10},{"id":245,"text":"\" We are not ready for even a small action size of Libya much less Korean War 2.0 , \"","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"Nance said in a tweet .","depth":11},{"id":247,"text":"\" This talk of Locked & Loaded is irresponsible madness . \"","depth":10},{"id":248,"text":"Donald Trump loyalists","depth":5},{"id":249,"text":"eager to back up his rhetoric on North Korea","depth":5},{"id":250,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":251,"text":"However , large-scale air , sea and land exercises are planned for later this month ,","depth":6},{"id":252,"text":"which could ratchet tensions up further .","depth":6},{"id":253,"text":"Trump was due to interrupt his working holiday for a lightning visit to Washington on Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":254,"text":"according to one report .","depth":7},{"id":255,"text":"But it was not clear","depth":7},{"id":256,"text":"whether the trip was connected to the North Korean stand-off ,","depth":8},{"id":257,"text":"and there are secure facilities at his Bedminster golf club","depth":9},{"id":258,"text":"where he can discuss national security matters .","depth":9},{"id":259,"text":"The North Korean military has said","depth":6},{"id":260,"text":"its planned missile test","depth":8},{"id":261,"text":"aimed at the sea around Guam","depth":8},{"id":262,"text":"will be ready for launch on orders of the country ' s leader from mid-August .","depth":7},{"id":263,"text":"In his remarks , however , Mattis repeatedly underlined the role of diplomacy and non-military pressure on Pyongyang , and the key roles","depth":7},{"id":264,"text":"played by the secretary of state , Rex Tillerson , and the US envoy to the United Nations , Nikki Haley .","depth":7},{"id":265,"text":"\" You can see the American effort is diplomatically led , \"","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"Mattis said .","depth":8},{"id":267,"text":"He added :","depth":9},{"id":268,"text":"\" It has diplomatic traction .","depth":10},{"id":269,"text":"It is gaining diplomatic results .","depth":10},{"id":270,"text":"And I want to stay right there right now . \"","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":541,"left":384,"right":540,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":384,"left":285,"right":383,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":278,"right":281,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":274,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":273,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":0,"right":272,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":272,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":4,"right":276,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":276,"left":5,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":8,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":12,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":383,"left":287,"right":382,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":382,"left":360,"right":381,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":360,"left":293,"right":359,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":290,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":18,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":19,"right":288,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":22,"right":291,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":359,"left":322,"right":358,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":322,"left":318,"right":321,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":318,"left":307,"right":317,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":307,"left":299,"right":306,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":294,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":297,"right":31,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":30,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":27,"right":295,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":295,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":306,"left":32,"right":305,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":300,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":33,"right":34,"relat